## Backend Infrastructure

### Authentication & Middleware

#### [AuthMiddleware.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/dist/php_backend/middleware/AuthMiddleware.php)

**Enterprise-grade authentication layer:**

```php
// Core Methods:
requireAuth()                              // Session verification + account status check
requireRole($role)                         // Role-based access control
requirePermission($resource, $action)      // Granular RBAC enforcement
getUserPrimaryRole($userId)                // Get highest priority role
canOverride($adminId, $targetUserId)      // Admin hierarchy validation
logAudit($userId, $action, ...)           // Automatic audit trail logging
```

**Features:**
- Automatic session validation
- Suspended/inactive account blocking
- Multi-role support per user
- JSON response standardization
- IP address + user agent tracking

#### [PermissionManager.php](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/ldm_test/dist/php_backend/includes/PermissionManager.php)

**Helper utilities for RBAC:**

```php
hasPermission($userId, $resource, $action)  // Check permission
getUserPermissions($userId)                  // List all user permissions
getRolePriority($roleName)                   // Get hierarchy level
canManageUser($adminId, $targetUserId)      // Validate admin override rights
assignRole($userId, $roleName, $assignedBy) // Assign roles with tracking
```

